.*             THE QEDIT MACRO WILL ISSUE SVC 34                        26000018
.*                                                                      26050000
.*       TO ADD OR FREE AN ELEMENT OF A CIB QUEUE                       26400018
.*             WITH (0) = +ORIGIN AND (1) = -BLOCK                      26800018
.*                                                                      26850000
